============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

PREDICTIVE_SRE_ENABLED=true
PREDICTIVE_SRE_MODE=advisory
PREDICTIVE_SRE_DRY_RUN=true
PREDICTIVE_SRE_FAIL_CLOSED=true
PREDICTIVE_SRE_MIN_CONFIDENCE=0.60

ANOMALY_DETECTION_ENABLED=true
INCIDENT_PREDICTION_ENABLED=true
SLO_FORECASTING_ENABLED=true
ERROR_BUDGET_FORECASTING_ENABLED=true
CAPACITY_PLANNING_ENABLED=true
RELIABILITY_ADVISOR_ENABLED=true

OPTIMIZATION_CENTER_ENABLED=true
OPTIMIZATION_MODE=advisory
OPTIMIZATION_DRY_RUN=true
OPTIMIZATION_REQUIRE_APPROVAL=true
OPTIMIZATION_EXECUTION_ENABLED=false
OPTIMIZATION_FAIL_CLOSED=true

FINOPS_ENABLED=true
COST_OPTIMIZATION_ENABLED=true
COST_OPTIMIZATION_DRY_RUN=true
WORKLOAD_PLACEMENT_ENABLED=true
WORKLOAD_PLACEMENT_DRY_RUN=true

GROWTH_INTELLIGENCE_ENABLED=true
CUSTOMER_HEALTH_PREDICTION_ENABLED=true
CHURN_SIGNAL_ENABLED=true
EXPANSION_SIGNAL_ENABLED=true
PARTNER_GROWTH_ENABLED=true
RESELLER_PERFORMANCE_ENABLED=true
MARKETPLACE_RANKING_ENABLED=true
REGIONAL_EXPANSION_RECOMMENDER_ENABLED=true

EXECUTIVE_COMMAND_CENTER_ENABLED=true
QBR_REPORTS_ENABLED=true
EXECUTIVE_SUMMARY_ENABLED=true
PORTFOLIO_RISK_ENABLED=true

PREDICTION_DATA_RETENTION_DAYS=180
OPTIMIZATION_RECOMMENDATION_RETENTION_DAYS=180

Rules:
- Predictive SRE must be advisory by default.
- Optimization execution must be disabled by default.
- Cost optimization must be dry-run by default.
- Workload placement must be dry-run by default.
- Forecast confidence must be included in all predictive outputs.
- Low-confidence predictions must be marked as advisory-only.
- No automated optimization may execute unless approved.
- No optimization may violate residency, tenant isolation, billing, governance, or GA safety gates.
- No raw customer payloads, secrets, or credentials may be used in prediction outputs.

